{
  "stem": "24111.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Horst-Wessel-Lied, the song of Horst-Wessel was a song, and one sentence is till the Jews' blood drips from our knives.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that an-- that was a shock for me, because I went to a public school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say all, or most of my friends, were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In my particular class, we were only two Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All other children were Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our Jewish [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] education was once or twice a week for an hour or two.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Jewish children in this particular school, which is called Renngasse Hauptschule were brought together into one class room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And an rabbi from the Jewish community came and gave us religious [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] introduction.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went only very infrequently to the temple, although I had bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And also my grandparents observed all the Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But my father and my close family was not really, you know, by no means orthodox.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were more what was called reformed Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Austria is to the largest extent an Catholic country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that is also the national religion, and all other religions were small minorities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I believe in-- in Vienna, by March 1938, there were only perhaps 200,000 Jews living.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and the rest were Catholic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of them were Catholic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I really don't recall that I ever experienced antisemitism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But now that you mention that, I remember there were a few German Jewish refugees coming to my father before the 1938 invasion of Austria, and they came from Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told us many stories, which neither he or I or everybody else really believed them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was stories of beginning atrocities of Jews sent to detaining camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
